# Mosquitto ACL (usernames only — no secrets; passwords live in ./passwd).
# Least privilege now that the broker is exposed on the LAN.

# Zigbee2MQTT: its own tree only.
user z2m
topic readwrite zigbee2mqtt/#

# Home Assistant: the automation hub — full broker access.
user hass
topic readwrite #

# Ultra-Magners (Windows PC) focus agent: read-only on the focus topic, nothing else.
user ultra-magners
topic read focus/#
